    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a meticulously maintained vehicle that balances performance with sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and optimal road-handling capabilities. The exterior retains a professional finish, while the interior remains refined and well-appointed. Engineered for longevity and reliability, this vehicle represents a premier choice for the discerning driver seeking quality and value in a pre-owned executive class automobile.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
